data.title: Visa's (V) Q2 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
data.text: Visa's (V) Q2 earnings beat on perked up volumes despite the coronavirus breakdown.

data.title: Visa cites rising unemployment as it withdraws full-year financial guidance
data.text: Visa Inc. (NYSE: V) released its second-quarter earnings report on Thursday that posted a 4% increase in profit. The company, however, cited rising unemployment due to COVID-19 as it withdrew its full-year financial guidance.

data.title: Visa withdraws annual outlook amid virus outbreak
data.text: Visa on Thursday decided to pull its full-year outlook on rising unemployment numbers and more people conserving cash during the Covid-19 pandemic even while posting a second-quarter profit that rose 4%.
